{"tid":635798,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"袁文傑：「似是情理之內，也是意料之外！」","createTime":"2018-04-20T10:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T11:46:19.000Z","uid":31314,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc54c1ac067557626c553e5109f7aebd9444455d","tid":635798,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"「似是情理之內，也是意料之外！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://上週on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%8A%E9%80%B1on.cc&d=tFF4iT3s6TCW%2BZfnjzo1lEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=820cc5ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">上週on.cc</a>老編想我對雲加今時今日狀況寫幾句，馬上想到，大時代股神必勝法&mdash;-「及早離去」！<br />\n<br />\n雲加對阿仙奴之重要性不言而喻，沒有他，沒有今天的英超；沒有他，阿仙奴未必跟得上時代步伐，甚或被甩掉在後頭⋯⋯一位技戰術的引領風潮者，可是，因為球會財力負擔，這個問題所帶來連串已非陣容人腳帶來之深層震盪，令雲加「退化」得很快，也令人不忍......<br />\n<br />\n這篇報導出街時，仍未進行作客1:2負紐卡素之比賽，就在賽後，雲加表示球隊攻守失去平衡，老實說，到了季尾，仍説這些話，那是蒼白得可以之無力感！到本週四（昨天）舉行的記者會，雲加一再被傳媒問到今後他在阿仙奴的處境，他居然沒有慣常的「會履行餘下合約」作回應，反而，令我感到一些不妥⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n是的，作為支持了阿仙奴數十年的我，總會以為自己某些時候可與球會「心領神會」，只是，沒意料到，不足24小時，推測竟速成事實。這是「及早離去」嗎？大膽説句，其實，也已經遲了，這肯定是對雲加一種遺憾⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n作為球迷，會經常想念某某球星與自己一同成長，但教練呢？我相信，雲加，是為數不多的可與各位球迷一同起跌多年的老朋友，而作為阿仙奴球迷，我可以很感光榮的曾經擁有雲加。<br />\n<br />\n心情很難平伏，感謝雲加先生，放手並非絕無意義！<br />\n<br />\n文傑"},{"pid":"a686c87df303bc285c1ec80335d92f3c66d3ea6f","tid":635798,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b71a7b6b3d86ff1b8b6d23e2cf428a0d96853f","tid":635798,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"文傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59aaec5c15f44e7cfb4ce8920588d945b80508f","tid":635798,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e855cb757ba2f869492119d9cffdfd05731c024","tid":635798,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"Man kit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f287fe29953e4308021055b55b5ab0494f8f2f84","tid":635798,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e878f3c2485365d3efb0a28f456a913cb4766c42","tid":635798,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}